description: [``botocore``] Added custom request handling and custom response support in rule actions and default action; Added the option to inspect the web request body as parsed and filtered JSON.
[``botocore``] AWS Identity and Access Management GetAccessKeyLastUsed API will throw a custom error if customer public key is not found for access keys.
[``botocore``] Allow Dots in Registry and Schema Names for CreateRegistry, CreateSchema; Fixed issue when duplicate keys are present and not returned as part of QuerySchemaVersionMetadata.
[``botocore``] This release adds support for Event Subscriptions to DocumentDB.
[``botocore``] Amazon Location added support for specifying pricing plan information on resources in alignment with our cost model.
